  <br />
  <em>Arms and Flag of <a href="pl-kp-wn.html">Wielka Nieszawka</a>, Poland (fotw)</em>
  </dd>
  
  <hr /><a name="powdered"></a>
  <dt style="font-weight: bold">POWDERED</dt>
  <dd>1) In vexillology a term sometimes used to describe a number of small (usually but not invariably) identical charges scattered across the field of a flag.<br>
  2) In heraldry see &lsquo;<a href="vxt-dvs2.html#seme">sem&eacute;</a>&rsquo;. 
  <p>
  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d1537.gif">
