  <a href="../images/v/vxt-d4845.gif">
  <img src="../images/v/vxt-d4845.gif" border="0" alt="powdered" height="108"></a>
  <br />
  <em><a href="fr_mon.html#lis">Banner of France</a> c1150 � c1350 (fotw);
  Flag of <a href="be-wbrch.html">Chastre</a>, Belgium (fotw); 
  Flag of <a href="fr-r-bf.html">Bourgogne-Franche-Comt�</a>, France (fotw)
  </em></dd>
  
